        <p class="main_text">Need a car to meet you in another city when you travel the country or abroad? Want a polite knowledgeable driver to chauffeur you? Wish the service would match the same high caliber you've become accustomed to in your local area? </p>
        <p class="main_text">Now you can travel with Apex beyond Miami , NY , and LA with Worldwide Service from Apex International. </p>
